data.description: Move fast to see this gated golf community gem-comfortable and bright. Spotless and upgraded. New roof. Remodeled kitchen with black stainless steel appliances. Master bedroom with walk-in closet and remodeled master bathroom. Fenced patio with a beautiful landscape & added paves. Electrical and manual accordion shutters. Outdoor lights.  Alarm system. Excellent schools, close to I-75, Wholefoods market and Pembroke Garden Shops. Roving Patrol and  school bus pick up at Grove entrance.  Reinforced garage door.
data.whatILove: Move fast to see this gated golf community gem-comfortable and bright. Stunning high ceilings, wood floor, white walls.  Master bedroom with walk-in closet.  New kitchen with black stainless steel appliances. Fenced patio with a beautiful landscape & added paves. Electrical and manual accordion shutters.  Alarm and intercom system. Excellent schools, close to I-75, Wholefoods market and Pembroke Garden Shops. Newer A/C. Roving Patrol and  school bus pick up at Grove entrance.  Reinforced garage door.
